OL,3,CApply now to work for ITV News in the
OL,4,CChannel Islands
OL,6,FThe prestigious ITV Academy News
OL,7,FTraineeship 2024-2025 is now open for
OL,8,Fapplications and ITV Channel is one of
OL,9,F12 regions across the British Isles
OL,10,Flooking for someone with commitment
OL,11,Fand enthusiasm to join our team.
OL,13,FThe scheme provides opportunities for
OL,14,Fthose looking to start their career in
OL,15,Fnews and ITV is particularly
OL,16,Finterested in people who have
OL,17,Fcommitted themselves to a career in
OL,18,Fjournalism.
