OL,3,CApply now to work for ITV News in the
OL,4,CChannel Islands
OL,6,FThis can be either through their
OL,7,Fwriting, work experience or career to
OL,8,Fdate, as well as those people with an
OL,9,Finterest in journalism who are looking
OL,10,Ffor a career change.
OL,12,FShortlisted candidates will be invited
OL,13,Fto take part in a one-day online
OL,14,Fassessment on either Tuesday 23,
OL,15,FWednesday 24 or Thursday 25 April.
OL,17,FThe successful applicant for ITV
OL,18,FChannel will start a nine-month
OL,19,FTraineeship in Jersey on Monday 30
OL,20,FSeptember.
