OL,3,CApply now to work for ITV News in the
OL,4,CChannel Islands
OL,6,FWe are keen to receive applications
OL,7,Ffrom those who are from Black, Asian
OL,8,Fand minority ethnic backgrounds,
OL,9,Fdisabled people and those from lower
OL,10,Fsocioeconomic groups as we recognise
OL,11,Fthat individuals from these groups are
OL,12,Fcurrently underrepresented in our
OL,13,Findustry.
OL,15,FIndividuals should be over the age of
OL,16,F18 by 30 September 2024.
OL,18,FApplications opened on Monday 5
OL,19,FFebruary and close at 11:59pm on
OL,20,FSunday 25 February.
