OL,3,CApply now to work for ITV News in the
OL,4,CChannel Islands
OL,6,F"I've had so many experiences I never
OL,7,Fwould have dreamed were possible. I
OL,8,Fjoined a year and a half ago and I
OL,9,Fcan't believe I'm now the full-time
OL,10,Fweather presenter for the Channel
OL,11,FIslands! If it wasn't for the
OL,12,FTraineeship and getting to try out
OL,13,Fweather presenting during our final
OL,14,Fweek, I would never have known how
OL,15,Fmuch I enjoy this role or have had the
OL,16,Fconfidence to go for the job. I would
OL,17,Fhugely recommend the scheme for anyone
OL,18,Fkeen to get stuck in. It opens the
OL,19,Fdoor to so many new opportunities and
OL,20,Fyou meet friends and mentors for life."
