OL,3,CApply now to work for ITV News in the
OL,4,CChannel Islands
OL,6,F"Time has flown, it's been the most
OL,7,Fincredible experience. I've worked on
OL,8,Fsome of the biggest stories from
OL,9,Fcovering the Queen's death to Storm
OL,10,FCiaran, teachers' strikes and uproar
OL,11,Fin the States Chamber. This job has
OL,12,Fallowed me to experience roles and
OL,13,Ftasks that I could never think of
OL,14,Fdoing anywhere else. As a Jersey girl
OL,15,Fmyself, it has been incredible to
OL,16,Flearn in my home patch and represent
OL,17,Fmy community on and off screen.
OL,18,FApplying for the Traineeship was the
OL,19,Fbest decision of my career and I urge
OL,20,Fanyone interested to apply."
