OL,3,CApply now to work for ITV News in the
OL,4,CChannel Islands
OL,6,F"I joined ITV News in the middle of
OL,7,Fthe pandemic and it was a privilege to
OL,8,Fbe at the sharp end of one of the
OL,9,Fdefining stories in our lifetime. On
OL,10,Fmy first day in the office, I was
OL,11,Ftrusted to go out and gather
OL,12,Finterviews for the programme. The
OL,13,FTraineeship gives you the vital
OL,14,Fbuilding blocks for a career at ITV.
OL,15,FI've had opportunities to work and
OL,16,Freport on major stories for TV and
OL,17,Fonline, and senior staff have
OL,18,Fsupported me to work on longer-form
OL,19,Finvestigations. It's a no-brainer to
OL,20,Fapply, you never know what doors it
OL,21,Fmight open."
